    {
      "id": "RULE-038",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "功能必须闭环；若某条功能链路尚未闭环，必须在命令行为或输出中明确告知用户当前边界，不能默认让用户以为已完整支持。",
      "fingerprint": "fe4549194870",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": null,
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-27T03:14:10.300Z",
      "status": "active"
    },
    {
      "id": "RULE-039",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "开始任何真实开发任务前，严禁跳过 AIDA MCP bootstrap 检查；如果 AIDA MCP 不可用，必须先提示用户检查并启用当前宿主中的 AIDA MCP。",
      "fingerprint": "94050d537c65",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": null,
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-27T03:14:10.301Z",
      "status": "active"
    },
    {
      "id": "RULE-040",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "如果 AIDA MCP 可用，开始真实开发任务前必须先读取集中授权清单、向用户说明“提前授权是为了避免后续开发过程中被 AIDA 中断”，并优先使用 aida_bootstrap、aida_task、aida_record、aida_memory 这些聚合工具以减少授权弹窗。",
      "fingerprint": "b7cdf9e378b0",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": null,
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-27T03:14:10.302Z",
      "status": "active"
    },
    {
      "id": "RULE-041",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "Only enter the AIDA task flow and persist branch/module memory after actual repository changes begin. Do not record pure investigation, solution discussion, ordinary chat, local environment operations, or experiments that do not land in the repository as tasks, context, or memory. Rule-only sedimentation can proceed normally without creating a task.",
      "fingerprint": "b22374ea9937",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": null,
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-27T11:23:52.443Z",
      "status": "active"
    },
    {
      "id": "RULE-042",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "任何会生成可执行命令、处理冲突、或影响真实工具启动链路的改动，必须补充可运行样本或真实命令验证；禁止只依赖脑内推断、宽松包含断言或“看起来应该可用”的结论。对于 merge、migrate、build、import、MCP 启动命令等链路，至少覆盖一条真实样本回放或实际命令执行验证。",
      "fingerprint": "60fe5557eb45",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": null,
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-28T03:43:21.787Z",
      "status": "active"
    },
    {
      "id": "RULE-043",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "发布或隔离验证应优先隔离命令环境，不得为规避环境污染随意创建 git worktree；执行 git 命令前必须先确认写入范围与副作用，涉及 worktree、branch、index 的操作必须采用最小副作用方案。",
      "fingerprint": "8f3786f6d8c5",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": "DEV-01",
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-28T07:33:41.381Z",
      "status": "active"
    },
    {
      "id": "RULE-044",
      "category": "process",
      "content": "处理用户反馈或真实项目异常前，必须先梳理完整流程和业务边界；如果用户提出的修复方向可能不属于通用产品缺陷，必须先说明判断、风险和建议方案并与用户确认，不能直接把一次性现场修复写进通用代码。",
      "fingerprint": "61f0ef580183",
      "source": {
        "branch": "main",
        "deviation": "DEV-03",
        "author": "vito-long"
      },
      "createdAt": "2026-04-29T02:08:45.267Z",
      "status": "active"
    }
